Requirement specification Offline Multiplayer

2 players on the playfield
Both players will have the ability to move and jump freely around the playfield.
If players jump outside the playfield they “die”
When players “die” they re-spawn on a randomly chosen spawn point
If a player jumps on the other players head the bottom player dies.
A player can only jump once, however a player can jump again after landing on a players head.
Score
If a player dies by falling out of the map the player loses 1 point.
If a player kills another player, the killing player is awarded 1 point, killed player loses no points.
Score is drawn on a GUI
If a certain score is reached by one of the players, the game ends and the player that achieved the target score wins the game.
